Text: Re Your Amazoncom InquiryThank you for contacting us at Amazoncom We have received your email inquiry and will respond to it as quickly as possible In the meantime if you have questions about a recent order you can visit Your Account by clicking the link at the top of our web site or by accessing this URL youraccount Once there you can cancel or combine items from orders that have not yet entered the shipping process as well as change the shipping address payment method or shipping method of most pending orders If you have questions that do not pertain to an order or account please visit our online Help pages you may find the answers to many of your questions here help You dont need to reply to this email as we will be able to use your original message to answer your question We look forward to reading your message and will respond as quickly as possible Sincerely Amazoncom Customer Service
